              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Thin, metallic lithium targets were vacuum evaporated",
                "onto tungsten backings. Target thicknesses ranged",
                "from 7 to 20 keV for four MeV alpha's, corresponding",
